at.fhv.roomanizer.application
Class CheckInController

java.lang.Object
  at.fhv.roomanizer.application.CheckInController

public class CheckInController
extends java.lang.Object

The CheckInController is responsible for the correct sequence of functions during the Check-In. The functions will get called by the GUI Controller and it will send or get the requested data. At the end of the sequence an habitation object should be going to the persistance layer.

phils
